Personal planning and automated investing – a new approach

newSchwab Intelligent Advisory™
A new way to plan for your financial goals. Our unique approach combines personal advice from a Planning
                        Consultant, who is a CERTIFIED FINANCIAL PLANNER™ professional, with our powerful
                        online planning tool.
$25K to start. No commissions charged. Fees are 0.28% of assets enrolled except cash.

