Dedicated financial advice with a personal relationship1
We offer clients the option of a high-touch relationship to help you meet your financial goals. A Schwab
                    Financial Consultant can help you determine the right solution for you, based on your needs. 

Schwab Private Client™
We provide you a dedicated team that collaborates with you to create, and adjust a sophisticated strategy,
                        tailored to your goals. You always stay informed and in control.
$500k to start. Fees are 0.90% for equities and 0.70% for fixed income.

