					No-hassle, full-featured checking account
				

No ATM fees.Receive unlimited ATM fee reimbursements.1
No minimum balance.No monthly service fees.3
Free online bill pay and free checks.Pay bills online, and get standard checks and a Visa® Platinum Debit Card—all at no charge.


Competitive 0.15% APY.Earn 0.15% variable Annual Percentage Yield.2
FDIC-insured.Checking account is insured up to $250,000.4 


					When you open a Schwab Bank High Yield Investor Checking® account, it’s automatically linked to a Schwab One® brokerage account, which also has no account minimums and no monthly service charges.3



